{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Setup\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab Create a track and set your VST instrument.\par}
