{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 New Track Plus\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Creates a new track based on the {\b base name} of the {\b selected track} (or "TRACK" if nothing is selected).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab If the selected track is a {\b folder}, the new track is placed {\b after all of that folder\u8217's children}, so the new one is at the same hierarchical level as the folder track.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab If the selected track is a {\b child track}, the new track is placed {\b immediately after it}, preserving its {\b parent relationship}.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The new track {\b inherits the color} of the selected track (if the selected track has a custom color).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The newly created track is {\b auto-selected} after creation.\sa180\par}
}

